media:group.media:title: SciShow Tangents - Pee!
media:group.media:description:
SciShow Tangents is a lightly competitive science and comedy podcast brought to you by the people who make SciShow! Listen to more here: https://scishow-tangents.simplecast.com

When we started recording this episode about pee, it occurred to us that we had a perfectly good YouTube channel dedicated to Pee just gathering dust! So we recorded our Google Hangout and are posting an entire, uncut SciShow Tangents recording session for the first time ever! 

You can help support the show (and get a ton of bonus goodies, like exclusive episodes)  by becoming a patron on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/SciShowTangents
